_______________________________________________________________________________
"Psychometry"     
        This is the famous "object reading" ability of psychics.  It's
        an identify type power on the mud, displaying any magical info
        of an object and giving some vague impressions about whether it
        is a special item or not.  It sometimes provides less specific
        information than a more objective appraisal or mages' identify
        would, but will often give more overall information than either
        of them will.  You must interpret the messages it gives you
        well.  
 
SP Cost:  30		Guild Level:  3		Potential Points:  2

Command:  objectread <object>
